<br>
Breed: <%= @pet.breed %>
<br>
Weight: <%= @pet.weight %> lbs
<br>
License #: <%= @pet.license %>
<br>
Microchip #: <%= @pet.microchip %>
<br>
Species: <%= @pet.species %>
